		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:00:59,640",
				"to": "00:01:06,800"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 59640,
				"to": 66800
			},
			"text": " If they download the block, full node and it verifies it, tries to run it, it doesn't"
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:06,800",
				"to": "00:01:11,240"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 66800,
				"to": 71240
			},
			"text": " succeed, it would ignore that block."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:11,240",
				"to": "00:01:15,720"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 71240,
				"to": 75720
			},
			"text": " And of course full nodes include the miners."
		},
		{
			"timestamps": {
				"from": "00:01:15,720",
				"to": "00:01:23,480"
			},
			"offsets": {
				"from": 75720,
				"to": 83480
			},
			"text": " And if we add them in 51% of our miners are honest, then they won't build on a block that"
